/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:15:45.000Z","msg":"絲打講得啱呀 大半年已經搞成咁 <br />\n或者真係要諗下大家將來點相處到大半世 <br />\nlong d得越耐 要面對嘅難關係越多<br />\n包括定居地 錢 人際關係 職業 價值觀 文化等等<br />\n我覺得你地諗好先再考慮復合會好啲"},{"pid":"9f8485bad4ef099d08c7ea6d0d67fc03899f0921","tid":612332,"uid":120418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T07:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果係無了期long d 首先一定要有共同目標<br />\n你會去佢個邊，定佢會黎香港生活結束long d<br />\n而家大半年佢已經頂唔順望唔到將來<br />\n長痛不如短痛啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>絲打講得啱呀 大半年已經搞成咁 <br />\n或者真係要諗下大家將來點相處到大半世 <br />\nlong d得越耐 要面對嘅難關係越多<br />\n包括定居地 錢 人際關係 職業 價值觀 文化等等<br />\n我覺得你地諗好先再考慮復合會好啲</blockquote><br />\n啱呀<br />\n要雙方都肯繼續落去一齊行<br />\n而呢條路比一般情侶更難行"},{"pid":"c647f9eac7ec467afb63e3d0f00dfa6252b9ed4f","tid":612332,"uid":178979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89e4ab44a9ec9d4ce8f1943f49a786b62c8ac576","tid":612332,"uid":24854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T09:31:16.000Z","msg":"其實我地都有計劃架 大家都ok 然後有一日突然就話覺得行唔到落去..."},{"pid":"57f694a9677281d8f595745cf6b04cf22cff860e","tid":612332,"uid":34371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a744e93518310cb8d7360526e14f7d4f0eae17f2","tid":612332,"uid":178979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d9a7bc469aef3f65bdeba8ae9bb0e4181bfafda","tid":612332,"uid":34371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-31T20:37:23.000Z","msg":"之前long d 分手，等左差唔多三年，大家都由原本既地方去左另一個方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"所以最後都無一齊返？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T16:43:12.000Z","msg":"仲等緊"},{"pid":"54f4182dd21ca21ca9627810e1476c8c3aa90386","tid":612332,"uid":120418,"lik